headline: Unpacking Q1 Earnings: MetLife (NYSE:MET) In The Context Of Other Life Insurance Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at MetLife (NYSE:MET) and the best and worst performers in the life insurance industry.
